      "content": "i know i should see a doctor but my clinic is super far and it's such a hassle to get an appointment. honestly i feel like i'm just getting out of shape. do you think i could just try taking an extra puff of my salbutamol whenever i feel this way? or maybe taking it more often during the day to see if it helps fix the breathing issue?",
